data.description: This home is a rare find with a new roof and new paint inside and out. This wonderfully light, airy and spacious 3/2 home includes a large den with custom bookcase and a master suite with a sitting area, separate bath and tub, private toilet and his and hers closets. The rear of the home extends the living space to a large screened rear patio with a newly extended 12X45 concrete patio and a large, beautifully maintained rear yard with privacy fencing.  There is also a roomy 3 car garage for your extra storage space. A must see home!
